(47514, '5FB1A2DC-5CA7-4FBD-81B6-3B01C3D70EE5', 'Finally, by giving everyone a dart gun, social media deputizes everyone to administer justice with no due process. Platforms like Twitter devolve into the Wild West, with no accountability for vigilantes. A successful attack attracts a barrage of likes and follow-on strikes. Enhanced-virality platforms thereby facilitate massive collective punishment for small or imagined offenses, with real-world consequences, including innocent people losing their jobs and being shamed into suicide. When our public square is governed by mob dynamics unrestrained by due process, we don’t get justice and inclusion; we get a society that ignores context, proportionality, mercy, and truth.', 'David', 'Nitzan', '2022-04-24T13:04:32.624344'),
(47518, '3DBA334C-971C-49CF-9AD6-59B5B6BD4676', 'Why I️ choose you this week - three main themes come to mind. The first is around play. When Orli suggested we become a “family of unicorns,” I️ didn’t think for a second you wouldn’t be game for that. I love that you love playing. And play is what makes us lighter and creates the space for laughter and sweetness.   The second is around empathy and compassion. I️’m incredibly grateful to have you as such a thoughtful and generous partner as I struggled with such deep sadness on Wednesday after finding out that I am loosing my one of my two favorite colleagues in the world. You comforted me and understood me, through my tears. I️’m grateful for your tenderness and for asking how I️’m doing. You made time to hear me and listen.   The third is related to sharing important readings and engaging intellectually. I was so glad you offered to have me read the Atlantic article on your phone during the flight. It was a long and thought provoking piece. One that I️’m not sure I️ would have had time to read this week. I appreciated that you saw a way to help me find a space to read it. I️ appreciate so very much that you want our intellectual and emotional lives to be interwoven. I love when you share things you are thinking about and bring me into your head.   With these three themes, it’s been a wonderful week. I’m still relishing the delight in seeing our 5 year old react to talking bears, hug Disney characters, steer space ships, and shoot flying objects. We live life so fully together and I️ don’t take that for granted, not for one second.', 'Nitzan', 'David', '2022-04-24T21:07:41.260631'),
